# PLACEHOLDER: Replace with the real Meridian cosign public key (PEM format).
#
# To generate a cosign keypair:
#   cosign generate-key-pair
#   This produces:
#     cosign.key  — private key (store as GHA secret COSIGN_PRIVATE_KEY)
#     cosign.pub  — public key  (replace this file and commit)
#
# This file is served at https://pkg.mdn.opennms.com/gpg/cosign.pub
# (no authentication — public-unauthenticated route via Traefik /gpg/ prefix)
#
# Subscribers use it for offline verification:
#   cosign verify \
#     --key /etc/meridian/cosign.pub \
#     --insecure-ignore-tlog \
#     pkg.mdn.opennms.com/oci/meridian-core:2025
#
# DO NOT commit the private key (cosign.key). Store it exclusively as the
# GHA secret COSIGN_PRIVATE_KEY.
